{"word":"σιτίζω","slug":"σιτίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>σιτίζω</b></el> <el>(σῑτίζω,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:σῖτος'><el>σῖτος</el></a>\n<p/><i>to feed, nourish, fatten</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> = <a href='S:σιτέομαι'><el>σιτέομαι</el></a>, <i>to eat</i>, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b><p/>"}]}